    "date": "2022-10-05T20:04:40Z",
    "text": "Comprehensive Southern Border Strategy Act\n\nThis bill requires the Department of Homeland Security to report to Congress a comprehensive southern border strategy. The strategy must include (1) an overview of current security risks along the southern border; and (2) an assessment of the barriers, technologies, and tools that are necessary to achieve and maintain situational awareness and operational control of the border."
